name: Control Box
tagline: Get the best out of your Android
body:
## Hey, you!  
  
Well... This is just a landing page for the GitHub repository for ControlBox. In future I will also put download Links for builds here, but as I am still in beta there are none yet (but you can always build yourself).
  
Currently the app also hasn't got so many features... But with your Help we can make it **GREAAAT**\! You can do so by either giving feedback to me or by helping as a dev for the app\!
  
___

###~ Till Kottmann (Deletescape)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
